                        <locus target="228rb">Fol. 228rb</locus><p>Fol. 228rb: <span style="font-size: large;">&#4632;&#4621;&#4768;&#4961; &#4925;&#4626;&#4936;&#4961; &#4829;&#4757;&#4721;&#4961; &#4632;&#4925;&#4624;&#4936;&#4961; &#4672;&#4758;&#4755;&#4961; &#4824;&#4941;&#4725;&#4624;&#4961; &#4789;&#4752;&#4756;&#4961; &#4629;&#4877;&#4961; &#4632;&#4658;&#4624;&#4810;&#4725;&#4961; &#4704;&#4821;&#4616;&#4720;&#4961; &#4656;&#4757;&#4704;&#4725;&#4961; &#4768;&#4632;&#4961; &#4819;&#4641;&#4649;&#4961; &#4616;&#4808;&#4653;&#4739;&#4961; &#4632;&#4661;&#4776;&#4648;&#4637;&#4961; &#4704;&#4978;&#4987;&#4983;&#4808;&#4972;&#4961; &#4819;&#4632;&#4720;&#4961; &#4656;&#4635;&#4821;&#4723;&#4725;&#4961; &#4757;&#4921;&#4624;&#4757;&#4961; &#4672;&#4851;&#4634;&#4961; &#4808;&#4661;&#4720;&#4961; &#4637;&#4853;&#4648;&#4961; &#4877;&#4709;&#4925;&#4962; &#4808;&#4779;&#4821;&#4704;&#4961; &#4720;&#4925;&#4629;&#4936;&#4961; &#4813;&#4661;</span> [fol. 228va] <span style="font-size: large;">&#4720;&#4961; &#4709;&#4628;&#4653;&#4752;&#4961; &#4770;&#4725;&#4846;&#4917;&#4843;&#4961; &#4704;&#4984;&#4987;&#4961;&#4808;&#4969;&#4987;&#4969;&#4961; &#4985;&#4808;&#4969;&#4961; &#4819;&#4632;&#4720;&#4961; &#4819;&#4616;&#4637;&#4962; &#4808;&#4704;&#4970;&#4987;&#4983;&#4808;&#4973;&#4961; &#4819;&#4632;&#4720;&#4961; &#4637;&#4629;&#4648;&#4725;&#4962; &#4808;&#4773;&#4637;&#4819;&#4632;&#4720;&#4961; &#4645;&#4875;&#4812;&#4961; &#4704;&#4978;&#4987;&#4808;&#4975;&#4987;&#4985;&#4808;&#4969;&#4962; &#4808;&#4704;&#4978;&#4987;&#4808;&#4972;&#4987;&#4808;&#4973;&#4969;&#4961; &#4819;&#4632;&#4720;&#4961; &#4656;&#4635;&#4821;&#4723;&#4725;&#4962; &#4808;&#4773;&#4637;&#4720;&#4757;&#4704;&#4619;&#4725;&#4961; &#4704;&#4978;&#4987;&#4981;&#4808;&#4975;&#4961; &#4819;&#4632;&#4725;&#4962; &#4808;&#4720;&#4925;&#4629;&#4936;&#4961; &#4704;&#4824;&#4632;&#4752;&#4961; &#4635;&#4724;&#4814;&#4661;&#4961; &#4808;&#4757;&#4876;&#4619;&#4810;</span>&#8230;</p><foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                        <note>The scribe modified the embedded colophon of the work in including a date for the composition of the work in Egypt, which is Sunday, 10th of Mäskäräm, 1064 year of the martyrs (= September 1347 A.D.). He included also the dates of his work: 7181 year of the world (=1689 A.D.), 265 year of mercy (=1689 A.D.), 1681 year of the Incarnation (=1688-89 A.D.), 1405 year of the martyrs (=1688-89 A.D.), 1047 [sic] year of Hijra (=1637 A.D.), during the year of Matthew.</note>
                     </colophon>
